{"tid":2254708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BNO居英簽證 明年1.31起申請","createTime":"2020-10-23T04:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T04:43:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"58e0d1638e840eec348c8b09148e38e34bfd64c7","tid":2254708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/NEVGQOAD2NAVNEABCCF3XOOLN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FNEVGQOAD2NAVNEABCCF3XOOLN4%2F&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRDnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=b8e5b567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201023%2FNEVGQOAD2NAVNEABCCF3XOOLN4%2F&h=b3618071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201023/NEVGQOAD2NAVNEABCCF3XOOLN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nBNO居英簽證 明年1.31起申請<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京落實港版國安法後，英國政府讓擁有英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）資格的港人及家庭受養人最快六年可入籍英國。英國政府昨日公佈，BNO簽證明年1月31日起接受申請，不設配額。英國外交部及內政部發聲明稱，所有具BNO資格者及其家庭受養人，只要通常居住在香港，即符合資格申請BNO簽證；毋須持有有效BNO護照，申請時可使用香港特區護照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RI_ea6g4rNOWM1qqiI8Nug6bwFs=/507x728/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OWQRGNISVNBKNPPXYPD2GFD3B4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRI_ea6g4rNOWM1qqiI8Nug6bwFs%3D%2F507x728%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOWQRGNISVNBKNPPXYPD2GFD3B4.jpg&h=4eafbbfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBNO<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五年簽證需250鎊<br />\n<br />\n費用方面，五年簽證為250英鎊（約2,540港元）， 申請人亦可以選擇申請30個月期簽證，費用為180英鎊（約1,829港元）。像其他移居英國的人一樣，BNO公民須支付移民醫療附加費，才可使用英國國家衞生服務（NHS）。另外要提供結核病檢驗證書，並須證明自己及家庭受養人有經濟能力，能在英國生活至少六個月。<br />\n<br />\n申請者必須沒有嚴重的刑事犯罪紀錄，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nBNO簽證持有人在英居住五年後，只。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港總領事賀恩德（Andrew Heyn）表示：「。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vgWbVnwSoCQTyUt8HxsB6GkQ6fc=/489x702/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BE2VN27TP5BQXN5NY647G66TPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvgWbVnwSoCQTyUt8HxsB6GkQ6fc%3D%2F489x702%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBE2VN27TP5BQXN5NY647G66TPY.png&h=3a1587d4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}